{
  "name": "RPlog_Many_Thoughts_Little_Words",
  "title": "Many Thoughts, Little Words",
  "summary": "On a cold Tatooine night, the silver-eyed Nagai woman Ash Seneal notices a hooded man, the hunter Mithral, shadowing her through the streets and alleys. Recognizing him as a deliberate pursuer, she leads him into a confrontation, each silently analyzing and profiling the other as their wary game of limits escalates. A thrown grenade and a running brawl follow, the two trading blows, blades, and a shotgun in a vicious, evenly matched fight that leaves both wounded. Beneath the violence runs a current of mutual fascination and grudging respect, their terse exchanges circling trust, respect, and Ash's interest in training. They withdraw to a quiet private clinic to have their injuries tended, where Mithral keeps her primed with hints of more to come, and Ash, battered but composed, weighs the intriguing implications of his offer.",
